Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/30/012638_5d01168cf6771ade2cb15ac15d65a60b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F30%2F012638_5d01168cf6771ade2cb15ac15d65a60b.jpg&h=44087235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人知圖中既類似款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想要day con <br />\n好少帶冇咩留意 唔該曬大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5h04662.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5h04662.jpg&h=5d8f868f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nEver color signature 1day"},{"pid":"ba52d66d5efd8c5e057df7793f1b4a82833d2f2a","tid":222352,"uid":105002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以前中學mk時代有戴過格仔鋪既con<br />\n發現著色直徑大少少就好唔襯自己 好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後試過好幾隻colorcon都伏左（one day acuvue, user select etc.)<br />\n當中唯一得freshlook既day con係岩岩好<br />\n睇返著色直徑原來得12.8mm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但想買2weeks以上 有無絲打會有推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打係咪少/唔化妝?</blockquote><br />\n我諗係個樣既問題 大少少會好怪 好似謝安琪套疆咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會係你揀d款太實色 無乜pattern"},{"pid":"af4ce52deef6a79e49c1884c240d0b4f4bb030a8","tid":222352,"uid":74088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以前中學mk時代有戴過格仔鋪既con<br />\n發現著色直徑大少少就好唔襯自己 好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後試過好幾隻colorcon都伏左（one day acuvue, user select etc.)<br />\n當中唯一得freshlook既day con係岩岩好<br />\n睇返著色直徑原來得12.8mm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但想買2weeks以上 有無絲打會有推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打係咪少/唔化妝?</blockquote><br />\n我諗係個樣既問題 大少少會好怪 好似謝安琪套疆咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會係你揀d款太實色 無乜pattern</blockquote><br />\n漸變嗰啲好j到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> olens russian velvet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過上眼就係另一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n建議絲打唔好揀外面有個黑環嗰類款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好易出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381067dfc2d710fe0cde7fb0e7701a8845361d5f","tid":222352,"uid":107909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:45:46.000Z","msg":"聽左大家既建議 買左一對olens既cinnamon 試試<br />\nolens好多細環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n13.0mm 無黑環既橙色（佢話brown)<br />\n上眼都唔錯 大細剛好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9b4f11037ce4dff882d2a0182246c9d2e27bcc","tid":222352,"uid":107909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:46:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以前中學mk時代有戴過格仔鋪既con<br />\n發現著色直徑大少少就好唔襯自己 好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後試過好幾隻colorcon都伏左（one day acuvue, user select etc.)<br />\n當中唯一得freshlook既day con係岩岩好<br />\n睇返著色直徑原來得12.8mm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但想買2weeks以上 有無絲打會有推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打係咪少/唔化妝?</blockquote><br 